menuconfig WDT_SOFTWARE
	bool "Additional software watchdog for more channels"
	depends on IWDG_STM32
	help
	  Enable software watchdog

	  The software watchdog allows to have individual watchdog channels
	  per thread, even if the hardware supports only a single watchdog.

config WDT_SOFTWARE_CHANNELS
	int "Maximum number of software watchdog channels"
	depends on WDT_SOFTWARE
	default 5
	range 2 100
	help
	  The timeouts for each channel are stored in an array. Allocate only
	  the required amount of channels to reduce memory footprint.
